ygData.messageBody:
Hiya guys!

I've been spending way too much time playing. Last night my cleric on
bertoxx made 42nd level. She's doing really well. I've also been spending a
lot of time helping people in my guild with quests and camping for items.
All my guildmates chipped in a got me a Runed Mith breastplate! I couldn't
believe it! wooohooo I'm having way too much fun. Come visit me if you're on
bertox! Elahana Sunsoar's the name and you can usually find me around Lower
guk or somewhere in faydark.
Hope everyone's doing well

Romney
Elahana
